Go inside folder Threejs and do 

npm run build

Then, go to a shell and do

ipconfig

Extract the IPv4 Address. E.g.

C:\Users\aml>ipconfig

Windows IP Configuration
...
Ethernet adapter Ethernet:

   Connection-specific DNS Suffix  . :
   Link-local IPv6 Address . . . . . : fe80::17c:9c63:8be6:2487%8
   IPv4 Address. . . . . . . . . . . : 192.168.2.79
   Subnet Mask . . . . . . . . . . . : 255.255.255.0
   Default Gateway . . . . . . . . . : 192.168.2.1

Start a browser and go to

http://192.168.2.79:8900


